{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# BTC Short-Horizon Phased Roadmap\n\nEvery phase past Phase 1 is gated on **evidence**, not schedule. Failing a gate is a valid outcome.",
      "x": -600,
      "y": -600,
      "width": 680,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "p1",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Phase 1 — Paper MVP\n\n**Status:** DONE (merged 2026-04-24)\n\nWorker thread scans btc-updown-(5m|15m)-<ts>, estimates P(up) via Φ(d₂), records paper trades, resolves on window close, exposes `polyagent btc5m-stats`.\n\n**Remaining:** deploy migration 005, enable, optionally apply for sponsored Chainlink key.",
      "x": -600,
      "y": -440,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "p2",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Phase 2 — Live trading\n\n**Gate (all three, at 14-day mark):**\n- Total P&L ≥ $5\n- Win rate ≥ 52%\n- Basis mis-resolutions ≤ 1 per 100\n\n**Build:** BTC5M_LIVE_ENABLED flag, bankroll cap, per-day loss kill switch, fixed $5 size → Kelly after 50 trades.\n\n**Effort:** ~1 day",
      "x": -200,
      "y": -440,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "p3",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Phase 3 — Chainlink swap\n\n**Gate:** live basis eats ~1/3 of gross P&L, OR sponsored key arrives.\n\n**Build:** ChainlinkSpotSource subclass, config swap. Interface already designed for this — zero other code changes.\n\n**Effort:** ~1 day",
      "x": 200,
      "y": -440,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "p4",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Phase 4 — Latency (likely unnecessary)\n\n**Gate:** evidence of adverse selection — fills on ask right before price drops.\n\n**Build:** Coinbase WebSocket + possibly Polymarket WS.\n\n**Effort:** ~2–3 days (async in sync codebase).\n\n**Expected:** skip. 5m doesn't need it.",
      "x": -200,
      "y": -140,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "p5",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Phase 5 — Cross-tenor arb\n\n**Gate:** 5m + 15m both show edge AND observed cases of coverage-equivalent inconsistency (3×5m ≠ 1×15m pricing).\n\n**Build:** tenor-arb module, multi-market position tracker, joint-risk bookkeeping.\n\n**Effort:** ~1 week\n\n**Expected:** low-probability profit, useful as monitoring signal.",
      "x": 200,
      "y": -140,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "nongoals",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Explicit Non-Goals\n\n- **Asset expansion** (ETH/SOL/XRP/DOGE). BTC only; expand across time.\n- **ML trend classifier.** OddArb trap; won't transfer.\n- **LLM involvement.** Math > reasoning for quantitative markets.\n- **1-minute markets.** Not listed by Polymarket; different design.",
      "x": -600,
      "y": -140,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "fail",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Gate Fails ≠ Delete\n\nInfra costs ~zero (Coinbase polls).\nLeave it running. Re-evaluate monthly.\nIf Chainlink credentials arrive, basis story changes — retry.",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "classifier",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Parallel: main-bot classifier loop\n\nCompletely separate: the market classifier (sports/crypto/politics/macro/other) is accumulating per-class data on the slow bot. Its decision point is orthogonal — different instruments, different edge sources.",
      "x": -200,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "2"
    }
  ],
